<li id="cite_note-new_wilderness-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-new_wilderness_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-new_wilderness_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFKristen_Rogers-Iversen2007" class="citation news cs1">Kristen Rogers-Iversen (September 2, 2007). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://archive.sltrib.com/story.php?ref=/news/ci_6783958">"Utah settlers' black slaves caught in 'new wilderness'<span class="cs1-kern-right"></span>"</a>. The Salt Lake Tribune.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Utah+settlers%27+black+slaves+caught+in+%27new+wilderness%27&amp;rft.date=2007-09-02&amp;rft.au=Kristen+Rogers-Iversen&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.sltrib.com%2Fstory.php%3Fref%3D%2Fnews%2Fci_6783958&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACivil+rights+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
