<li id="cite_note-Fine-60"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Fine_60-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSmith1948" class="citation book cs1">Smith, George (1948). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://byustudies.byu.edu/content/volume-6-chapter-9"><i>History of the Church, Vol. 6</i></a>. Salt Lake City: Deseret Book Company. p.&#160;210<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">28 August</span> 2017</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=History+of+the+Church%2C+Vol.+6&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City&amp;rft.pages=210&amp;rft.pub=Deseret+Book+Company&amp;rft.date=1948&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=George&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbyustudies.byu.edu%2Fcontent%2Fvolume-6-chapter-9&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACivil+rights+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
