<li id="cite_note-61"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-61">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFSmith" class="citation web cs1">Smith, Joseph. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.josephsmithpapers.org/paper-summary/journal-december-1842-june-1844-book-3-15-july-1843-29-february-1844/265">"Journal, December 1842–June 1844; Book 3, 15 July 1843–29 February 1844"</a>. <i>Joseph Smith Papers</i>. LDS Church.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=Joseph+Smith+Papers&amp;rft.atitle=Journal%2C+December+1842%E2%80%93June+1844%3B+Book+3%2C+15+July+1843%E2%80%9329+February+1844&amp;rft.aulast=Smith&amp;rft.aufirst=Joseph&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.josephsmithpapers.org%2Fpaper-summary%2Fjournal-december-1842-june-1844-book-3-15-july-1843-29-february-1844%2F265&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACivil+rights+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
