<li id="cite_note-Interracial_Marriage-66"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Interracial_Marriage_66-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Interracial_Marriage_66-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Interracial_Marriage_66-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFMason" class="citation journal cs1">Mason, Patrick Q. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20180409205756/http://digitallibrary.utah.gov/awweb/awarchive?type=file&amp;item=12054">"The Prohibition of Interracial Marriage in Utah,1888-1963"</a>. <i>Utah Historical Quarterly</i>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://digitallibrary.utah.gov/awweb/awarchive?type=file&amp;item=12054">the original</a> on 2018-04-09<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2019-04-26</span></span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Utah+Historical+Quarterly&amp;rft.atitle=The+Prohibition+of+Interracial+Marriage+in+Utah%2C1888-1963&amp;rft.aulast=Mason&amp;rft.aufirst=Patrick+Q.&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fdigitallibrary.utah.gov%2Fawweb%2Fawarchive%3Ftype%3Dfile%26item%3D12054&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACivil+rights+and+Mormonism" class="Z3988"></span></span>
